# ─── Scratch / local-only — kept out of the public repo ───
# Scripted demo recorder (lives in the local working tree only;
# the recordings it produces feed the media library at
# ~/Videos/successor-media/, which is also intentionally outside
# the repo). Keep one canonical copy at ~/successor-promo-videos/.
scripts/walkthrough_demo.py

# Media binaries — don't ship a hundred MB of GIFs in the source
# tree. The README links to externally-hosted versions instead.
*.mp4
*.mov
*.webm
*.gif
*.mp3
*.wav

# Generated artifacts from local fiddling
/tmp_*
/scratch_*

# Local planning / private notes — keep internal scratch out of the repo
/plans/
/notes/
docs/*.local.md
